# Cursor Rules for teijigo-beer-time

## Project Overview

This is a music circle "定時後ビールタイム" (Teijigo Beer Time) official website.
It intentionally uses a retro 90s-style homepage design.

## Tech Stack

- Nuxt 4 + Vue 3 (Composition API with `<script setup>`)
- TypeScript
- Yarn 4 (Berry) - use `corepack enable` to activate
- Node.js 24.x (Active LTS)
- Vitest + Vue Test Utils for testing
- ESLint 9 (Flat Config) + Stylelint + Prettier

## Code Style

### Vue Components

- ALWAYS use `<script setup lang="ts">`
- Block order: `<script>` → `<template>` → `<style>`
- Component names in templates: kebab-case (`<tbt-h1>`)
- Use `<style scoped>`
- All components must have `Tbt` prefix (e.g., `TbtBlink.vue`)

### Example Component

```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
defineProps<{
  title: string
}>()
</script>

<template>
  <div class="my-component">
    <slot></slot>
  </div>
</template>

<style scoped>
.my-component {
  /* styles */
}
</style>
```

### TypeScript

- Avoid `any` type
- Prefix unused variables with `_`
- Leverage type inference

### CSS

- Class names: kebab-case
- No `!important`
- No vendor prefixes (autoprefixer handles it)
- Max nesting depth: 5

## Directory Structure

```
app/
├── components/
│   ├── atoms/       # Smallest components (Tbt prefix)
│   └── organisms/   # Composite components
├── pages/           # File-based routing
├── layouts/         # Layout components
└── resources/       # Static data
```

## Commands

```bash
yarn dev        # Dev server
yarn test       # Run tests
yarn lint       # Lint check
yarn lint:fix   # Auto-fix lint issues
```

## Important Notes

- Retro design (blink, marquee effects) is INTENTIONAL
- No UI libraries (Tailwind, Vuetify, etc.)
- Static site deployed to GitHub Pages
